{
  "text": "The solution proposed to this problem, the residual connection [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] tries to create shortcuts between nonconsecutive layers. However, the original additional residual connection (adding the input vector to the hidden representation) adds several constraints on the dimensionality of the hidden and input layers, which might require vector clipping [CITATION_3] , and it might lead to a loss of information.",
